---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SUPPORT_EMAIL } from "../../config/site";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Delete Account - Kafadar"
    description="How to permanently delete your Kafadar account and associated data."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Delete Account</h1>

        <article class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-7">
            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    1. In-App Deletion (Recommended)
                </h2>
                <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Open the Kafadar app.</li>
                    <li>Go to Profile or Settings.</li>
                    <li>Tap <strong>Delete My Account</strong>.</li>
                    <li>Confirm the deletion request to start processing.</li>
                </ol>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    2. Deletion by Email
                </h2>
                <p>
                    If you cannot access the app, send your request from your registered
                    email address to
                    <a
                        class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
                        href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a
                    >
                    with subject "Account Deletion Request".
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    3. Processing Time and Scope
                </h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        Verified requests are processed as quickly as reasonably possible.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Account data and user content are deleted or anonymized.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Some records may be retained if required by law.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">4. Important Note</h2>
                <p class="font-semibold text-red-600">
                    Deletion is irreversible. Quizzes and associated results may not be
                    recoverable.
                </p>
            </section>
        </article>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
